    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Nice! Couple of questions:\r\n- what is the actual behavior/willing behavior of the widget: what will it do in the end, browser wise, GA wise. What does it provides? I am a complete beginner with GA and I do not know the intents/goals/use case. This will help us identify the potential users.\r\n- why do you use a recurring setTimeout loop? What do you want to monitor?",
