    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Do we need to actually support multiple services (and possibly miss somes) or should we make it so that the widget exposes the necessary events/endpoint and it's easy to plug any analytics service into it?\r\n\r\nAPIs like \"services: ['ga', 'segment.io', 'gtm']\" are tricky to handle on the long run because we make ourselves dependant on their own APIs/configuration APIs.\r\n\r\nIf it makes sense, I would prefer having something that exposes the necessary API entries making it really easy to plug analytics services to search state. The rest being only documentation/guide for our users.",
